WEBVTT

00:19.019 --> 00:21.187
 <i>[eerie music playing]</i>

02:06.751 --> 02:08.753
 <i>[monks chanting]</i>

02:13.466 --> 02:15.969
 <i>[Faraday] Is this where we've</i>
 <i>been communicating from?</i>

02:16.010 --> 02:17.971
 <i>[Newton] Near enough.</i>
 <i>How's the machine?</i>

02:18.012 --> 02:19.472
 <i>[Justin] We almost died for it.</i>

02:19.514 --> 02:21.141
 <i>[Newton]</i>
 <i>Then I'm sure it's fine.</i>

02:21.182 --> 02:22.517
 <i>Did they shoot you?</i>

02:23.476 --> 02:25.395
 <i>-Yes.</i>
 <i>-Of course.</i>

02:25.436 --> 02:28.148
 <i>I believed I was</i>
 <i>returning to Anthea.</i>

02:28.189 --> 02:30.817
 <i>I needed to know our people</i>
 <i>were coming here.</i>

02:30.859 --> 02:32.652
 <i>-Our people?</i>
 <i>-I had a right.</i>

02:32.694 --> 02:35.488
 <i>Rights? You had</i>
 <i>a "right to the truth," did you?</i>

02:35.530 --> 02:37.782
 <i>You told me I was going home.</i>

02:37.824 --> 02:39.159
 <i>I want to go home.</i>

02:39.200 --> 02:40.493
 <i>So do I.</i>

02:40.535 --> 02:43.246
 <i>[gong sounding]</i>

02:44.956 --> 02:48.668
 <i>You know, they allow me</i>
 <i>to practice praying here.</i>

02:48.710 --> 02:51.671
 <i>It's the only thing I've been</i>
 <i>curious about for ages.</i>

02:51.713 --> 02:54.132
 <i>They allow me to be present,</i>

02:54.174 --> 02:58.344
 <i>so as you can see,</i>
 <i>I gave them our seeds.</i>

02:58.386 --> 03:00.722
 <i>I couldn't just be a shitlord,</i>

03:00.763 --> 03:02.182
 <i>take their water</i>
 <i>and breathe their air</i>

03:02.223 --> 03:04.225
 <i>and not give something.</i>

03:04.267 --> 03:06.561
 <i>And they opened themselves.</i>

03:06.603 --> 03:08.855
 <i>Most humans can't open</i>
 <i>themselves to us</i>

03:08.897 --> 03:10.815
 <i>without losing their</i>
 <i>fucking minds.</i>

03:10.857 --> 03:13.359
 <i>But these guys are divine.</i>

03:13.401 --> 03:15.945
 <i>Anyway, they're not</i>
 <i>a bundle of laughs.</i>

03:15.987 --> 03:18.406
 <i>But they're not bent</i>
 <i>on the destruction</i>

03:18.448 --> 03:20.283
 <i>of all living things, either.</i>

03:20.325 --> 03:22.368
 <i>[gong sounding]</i>

03:25.038 --> 03:26.039
 <i>[shushes]</i>

03:26.080 --> 03:28.541
 <i>[whispering] Vow of silence.</i>

03:28.583 --> 03:31.044
 <i>Don't pretend</i>
 <i>you're a child of God.</i>

03:31.085 --> 03:32.670
 <i>Maybe I am.</i>

03:32.712 --> 03:33.963
 <i>And listen to you.</i>

03:34.005 --> 03:35.882
 <i>I've created a monster.</i>

03:35.924 --> 03:38.218
 <i>All worked up over a lie.</i>

03:38.259 --> 03:39.886
 <i>I knew you'd tell her.</i>

03:39.928 --> 03:41.804
 <i>She wouldn't have</i>
 <i>done her bit if she knew.</i>

03:41.846 --> 03:45.225
 <i>-You don't know anything...</i>
 <i>-Anything about her.</i>

03:49.437 --> 03:50.897
 <i>Just show us why we're here.</i>

03:54.025 --> 03:57.946
 <i>[Newton] This geography has</i>
 <i>natural magnetic anomalies.</i>

03:57.987 --> 04:00.865
 <i>Their satellites go blind</i>
 <i>over me, which is...</i>

04:01.491 --> 04:02.909
 <i>Fitting.</i>

04:02.951 --> 04:05.912
 <i>The CIA's been</i>
 <i>missing me for years.</i>

04:05.954 --> 04:09.540
 <i>So now, it's just the gentlemen,</i>
 <i>and me.</i>

04:09.582 --> 04:10.625
 <i>And the quiet.</i>

04:12.168 --> 04:16.256
 <i>And our last fucking hope.</i>

04:17.215 --> 04:19.259
 <i>[ominous music playing]</i>

04:44.909 --> 04:46.536
 <i>[wind whistling]</i>

04:55.586 --> 04:57.463
 <i>[suspenseful music playing]</i>

05:08.683 --> 05:09.726
 <i>[Justin] The monks.</i>

05:09.767 --> 05:11.436
 <i>They must have</i>
 <i>built this with you?</i>

05:11.477 --> 05:14.856
 <i>[Newton] The parts were</i>
 <i>a fucking global scavenger hunt.</i>

05:14.897 --> 05:17.650
 <i>But the actual assembly</i>
 <i>isn't that complicated.</i>

05:17.692 --> 05:18.943
 <i>They found joy in it.</i>

05:19.527 --> 05:20.820
 <i>In creation.</i>

05:23.406 --> 05:24.532
 <i>It isn't big enough.</i>

05:25.992 --> 05:27.910
 <i>-For what?</i>
 <i>-[Faraday] The fusion device</i>

05:27.952 --> 05:29.829
 <i>is the engine for this ship.</i>

05:31.414 --> 05:34.542
 <i>You are going to fly it home</i>

05:34.584 --> 05:37.503
 <i>and bring the Antheans back.</i>
 <i>But not all of them.</i>

05:37.545 --> 05:39.130
 <i>[Newton] Don't be so</i>
 <i>fucking judgey.</i>

05:39.172 --> 05:40.340
 <i>The ship's fine.</i>

05:40.381 --> 05:42.175
 <i>Everybody's trying to kill me</i>
 <i>and I'm blind.</i>

05:42.216 --> 05:44.469
 <i>It's the best I could do</i>
 <i>with 45-years notice.</i>

05:44.510 --> 05:46.763
 <i>There were thousands</i>
 <i>when I left.</i>

05:46.804 --> 05:48.348
 <i>This ship will hold...</i>

05:48.389 --> 05:50.600
 <i>[sighs] Hundreds.</i>

05:52.226 --> 05:53.895
 <i>-Hundreds.</i>
 <i>-Which ones?</i>

05:55.730 --> 05:56.856
 <i>The adepts.</i>

05:57.982 --> 05:59.942
 <i>Not the drones.</i>

05:59.984 --> 06:01.402
 <i>-[Justin] Uh, but...</i>
 <i>-[Faraday] Just the adepts.</i>

06:01.444 --> 06:03.488
 <i>Well, of course,</i>
 <i>just the adepts.</i>

06:03.529 --> 06:05.698
 <i>I won't need drones here,</i>
 <i>will I?</i>

06:10.453 --> 06:11.496
 <i>[groans]</i>

06:12.455 --> 06:13.706
 <i>I can't see.</i>

06:14.582 --> 06:15.708
 <i>The drones have...</i>

06:15.750 --> 06:16.834
 <i>[whispering] We...</i>

06:18.252 --> 06:21.714
 <i>[in normal voice]</i>
 <i>We held Anthea together.</i>

06:21.756 --> 06:24.759
 <i>The clouds have gone</i>

06:24.801 --> 06:28.096
 <i>because of decisions</i>
 <i>adepts made!</i>

06:28.137 --> 06:30.973
 <i>There were 40 herd animals</i>
 <i>when I left.</i>

06:31.015 --> 06:32.558
 <i>Everything was stillborn.</i>

06:32.600 --> 06:35.353
 <i>Everything! Because of</i>
 <i>decisions you made!</i>

06:35.395 --> 06:36.562
 <i>In the name of progress.</i>

06:36.604 --> 06:38.106
 <i>This isn't even an argument.</i>
 <i>It's irrelevant.</i>

06:38.147 --> 06:39.399
 <i>[Faraday] Irrelevant?</i>

06:39.440 --> 06:41.859
 <i>There are only adepts</i>
 <i>because of us.</i>

06:41.901 --> 06:44.862
 <i>The adepts that are alive</i>
 <i>are alive because of us!</i>

06:44.904 --> 06:47.407
 <i>It was your names</i>
 <i>in the records.</i>

06:47.448 --> 06:49.367
 <i>But it was never ever you!</i>

06:49.409 --> 06:52.578
 <i>It was always our backs bending!</i>

06:52.620 --> 06:53.704
 <i>I trained you better than this.</i>

06:53.746 --> 06:55.415
 <i>I trained you!</i>

06:55.456 --> 06:58.334
 <i>I finally got it through</i>
 <i>my thick skull.</i>

06:58.376 --> 07:00.962
 <i>I trained you,</i>

07:01.003 --> 07:04.674
 <i>and too well if you think</i>
 <i>you can survive without us.</i>

07:04.715 --> 07:07.385
 <i>This is the ship we have!</i>

07:21.983 --> 07:24.444
 <i>[Justin] What... What happens</i>
 <i>to us when they get here?</i>

07:24.485 --> 07:25.695
 <i>[Newton] You will try</i>
 <i>and kill us all.</i>

07:25.736 --> 07:27.738
 <i>Yeah, after we try</i>
 <i>and kill you all.</i>

07:27.780 --> 07:29.615
 <i>Why won't you need drones here?</i>

07:29.657 --> 07:30.783
 <i>What happens to humans?</i>

07:34.078 --> 07:35.121
 <i>We'll...</i>

07:37.582 --> 07:38.833
 <i>We'll all be the drones?</i>

07:40.168 --> 07:41.961
 <i>What, like my... father?</i>

07:42.003 --> 07:43.671
 <i>Like my father</i>
 <i>who didn't know me?</i>

07:46.549 --> 07:49.302
 <i>Ms. Falls, before us,</i>

07:49.343 --> 07:52.472
 <i>your father was dying</i>
 <i>in a bed. Correct?</i>

07:52.513 --> 07:54.640
 <i>You lose something.</i>
 <i>You gain something--</i>

07:54.682 --> 07:55.808
 <i>You don't get to decide!</i>

07:55.850 --> 07:57.393
 <i>I didn't. You did.</i>

07:57.435 --> 07:59.770
 <i>You're already drones.</i>

07:59.812 --> 08:01.814
 <i>Humans will do anything</i>
 <i>as long as it confirms</i>

08:01.856 --> 08:03.649
 <i>something they need to believe</i>
 <i>about themselves, Ms. Falls.</i>

08:03.691 --> 08:06.027
 <i>Even you. He told you,</i>
 <i>you were special, you enlisted.</i>

08:06.068 --> 08:09.113
 <i>He told me we'd save everything.</i>
 <i>All of us.</i>

08:09.155 --> 08:10.448
 <i>And we are.</i>

08:10.490 --> 08:13.367
 <i>2030 is coming.</i>
 <i>The Earth will die.</i>

08:13.409 --> 08:15.745
 <i>Adepts and drones</i>
 <i>are a single system.</i>

08:15.786 --> 08:18.039
 <i>You can't yank them away</i>
 <i>from each other.</i>

08:18.080 --> 08:19.916
 <i>It's not what this is.</i>

08:19.957 --> 08:21.751
 <i>This is a connection.</i>

08:21.792 --> 08:24.545
 <i>Someone has to see,</i>
 <i>someone has to build.</i>

08:24.587 --> 08:26.631
 <i>You can't just change us</i>
 <i>to be what you need!</i>

08:26.672 --> 08:28.508
 <i>What we all need.</i>

08:28.549 --> 08:31.135
 <i>It's not magic. It's evolution.</i>

08:31.177 --> 08:33.721
 <i>My father is different.</i>

08:33.763 --> 08:35.765
 <i>All right? He is</i>
 <i>a fundamentally different--</i>

08:35.806 --> 08:36.849
 <i>Person.</i>

08:36.891 --> 08:38.434
 <i>Is he a person still?</i>

08:38.476 --> 08:40.937
 <i>And is it so terrible?</i>
 <i>He's alive.</i>

08:40.978 --> 08:42.396
 <i>You can love him.</i>

08:42.438 --> 08:46.359
 <i>Ms. Falls, I've had years</i>
 <i>with nothing to do but plan.</i>

08:46.400 --> 08:50.112
 <i>No walks to get a beignet,</i>
 <i>no monastery games night.</i>

08:50.154 --> 08:52.281
 <i>There is only one way.</i>

08:52.323 --> 08:54.825
 <i>We have to create</i>
 <i>the next version</i>

08:54.867 --> 08:56.327
 <i>of both our species.</i>

08:56.369 --> 08:59.038
 <i>Together, we'll thrive.</i>
 <i>Create the next--</i>

08:59.080 --> 09:00.498
 <i>-The next?</i>
 <i>-[Newton] It's like this jungle.</i>

09:00.540 --> 09:01.707
 <i>It's adapting.</i>

09:01.749 --> 09:03.417
 <i>Earth will be the next jungle.</i>

09:03.459 --> 09:06.128
 <i>And at this point,</i>
 <i>I say good riddance.</i>

09:06.170 --> 09:07.213
 <i>Onto the next thing.</i>

09:07.255 --> 09:09.423
 <i>We both fucked it!</i>

09:09.465 --> 09:10.508
 <i>2030.</i>

09:10.550 --> 09:13.386
 <i>This is how we all survive.</i>

09:13.427 --> 09:17.056
 <i>This is how your daughter's</i>
 <i>children have a chance.</i>

09:19.809 --> 09:22.019
 <i>No. No, I... I...</i>

09:23.062 --> 09:24.480
 <i>I can't open that door.</i>

09:25.565 --> 09:26.732
 <i>No.</i>

09:26.774 --> 09:28.317
 <i>If this is the end for us,</i>

09:28.359 --> 09:31.571
 <i>then we end as we are.</i>

09:31.612 --> 09:33.698
 <i>It's taken us forever</i>
 <i>to become who we are.</i>

09:35.199 --> 09:36.242
 <i>I know.</i>

09:39.870 --> 09:41.914
 <i>Don't you think I loved you</i>
 <i>when I came here?</i>

09:43.165 --> 09:45.126
 <i>I did.</i>

09:45.167 --> 09:47.920
 <i>I didn't have the words for it,</i>
 <i>but I did.</i>

09:47.962 --> 09:51.257
 <i>And you took my science</i>

09:51.299 --> 09:52.758
 <i>and my eyes,</i>

09:53.593 --> 09:55.636
 <i>and hunted me like an animal.</i>

09:57.430 --> 09:58.848
 <i>[Newton sighs]</i>

09:58.889 --> 10:00.975
 <i>All you had to do</i>
 <i>was love me back.</i>

10:04.437 --> 10:05.438
 <i>Now...</i>

10:07.315 --> 10:08.316
 <i>You...</i>

10:09.317 --> 10:10.610
 <i>Your family?</i>

10:11.944 --> 10:14.280
 <i>You're willing</i>
 <i>to lose your family?</i>

10:20.494 --> 10:22.288
 <i>[Newton] I'm going to rebuild</i>
 <i>our machine.</i>

10:22.330 --> 10:24.206
 <i>However, you changed</i>
 <i>the algorithm</i>

10:24.248 --> 10:26.375
 <i>that activates the core</i>
 <i>when you ran from the lab.</i>

10:26.417 --> 10:28.044
 <i>I would've certainly</i>
 <i>done the same thing.</i>

10:28.085 --> 10:29.629
 <i>I need you to unlock it.</i>

10:33.424 --> 10:37.094
 <i>It's hundreds of miles</i>
 <i>to anywhere.</i>

10:37.136 --> 10:39.597
 <i>A snake bite</i>
 <i>can take out your lungs</i>

10:39.639 --> 10:41.807
 <i>and you'll never see</i>
 <i>your family again.</i>

10:41.849 --> 10:44.018
 <i>If you unlock the algorithm,</i>

10:44.060 --> 10:45.853
 <i>you can go back to your life.</i>

10:45.895 --> 10:47.271
 <i>Your part is done.</i>

10:47.313 --> 10:48.689
 <i>We'll take care</i>
 <i>of the rest of it.</i>

10:48.731 --> 10:50.524
 <i>You won't see us anymore.</i>

10:50.566 --> 10:52.318
 <i>Us two, anyway.</i>

10:52.360 --> 10:55.029
 <i>Go back to being</i>
 <i>whoever you were.</i>

10:55.071 --> 10:57.990
 <i>Whoever you want.</i>
 <i>Shut the door.</i>

10:58.032 --> 11:01.452
 <i>Play music and dance together.</i>

11:01.494 --> 11:03.704
 <i>And treasure</i>
 <i>the time you still have.</i>

11:04.455 --> 11:07.667
 <i>Glances, voices...</i>

11:07.708 --> 11:11.962
 <i>You know what it is to pray</i>
 <i>for one more of any of those.</i>

11:14.840 --> 11:18.928
 <i>Time with people who matter,</i>
 <i>Ms. Falls.</i>

11:32.316 --> 11:33.359
 <i>[sniffles]</i>

11:36.404 --> 11:38.406
 <i>[breathes heavily]</i>

11:54.130 --> 11:57.091
 <i>[Wincamp] So, now there are</i>
 <i>two aliens in the wind.</i>

11:57.133 --> 11:58.926
 <i>We still don't have</i>
 <i>quantum fusion,</i>

11:58.968 --> 12:01.554
 <i>and this is your official report</i>

12:01.595 --> 12:03.097
 <i>on the end of Agent Clay.</i>

12:04.473 --> 12:06.434
 <i>Suicide.</i>

12:06.475 --> 12:09.478
 <i>Didn't Gregory Papel</i>
 <i>commit suicide as well?</i>

12:09.520 --> 12:11.313
 <i>Blew his brains out</i>
 <i>in the woods?</i>

12:11.355 --> 12:12.606
 <i>Yes, sir.</i>

12:12.648 --> 12:14.608
 <i>[Wincamp] Well, maybe one of you</i>
 <i>can tell me why</i>

12:14.650 --> 12:16.569
 <i>poking around in this mess</i>

12:16.610 --> 12:18.904
 <i>makes our operatives</i>
 <i>kill themselves?</i>

12:19.613 --> 12:20.823
 <i>Agent Dominguez?</i>

12:22.450 --> 12:23.909
 <i>I...</i>

12:23.951 --> 12:25.202
 <i>I really couldn't--</i>

12:25.244 --> 12:28.456
 <i>I think two tightly wound men</i>
 <i>became obsessed,</i>

12:29.081 --> 12:31.000
 <i>sir.</i>

12:31.041 --> 12:34.170
 <i>Clay was tightly wound,</i>
 <i>that's for sure.</i>

12:34.211 --> 12:37.047
 <i>Before your falling out,</i>
 <i>you and he were pretty close.</i>

12:37.089 --> 12:40.134
 <i>Am I gonna hear about</i>
 <i>you eating your gun, Drew?</i>

12:40.634 --> 12:42.094
 <i>At no time, sir.</i>

12:43.929 --> 12:45.097
 <i>Agent Dominguez?</i>

12:45.765 --> 12:46.807
 <i>No, sir.</i>

12:49.977 --> 12:51.562
 <i>[Wincamp]</i>
 <i>Find our missing friends,</i>

12:51.604 --> 12:53.773
 <i>and don't come back here</i>
 <i>with this again.</i>

12:53.814 --> 12:54.940
 <i>Are we clear?</i>

12:54.982 --> 12:56.025
 <i>[both] Yes, sir.</i>

13:06.744 --> 13:07.787
 <i>[sighs]</i>

13:11.874 --> 13:13.709
 <i>[Lisa] The coroner's report</i>
 <i>would've read</i>

13:13.751 --> 13:15.461
 <i>the first bullet went through</i>
 <i>Clay's jaw.</i>

13:16.587 --> 13:18.756
 <i>And second lodged in his chest.</i>

13:23.177 --> 13:24.470
 <i>Suicide means the Director</i>

13:24.512 --> 13:25.805
 <i>saw an altered report.</i>

13:30.017 --> 13:31.060
 <i>Thank you.</i>

13:32.853 --> 13:34.730
 <i>You're supposed to be smart.</i>

13:36.440 --> 13:38.776
 <i>Here's my take on all this.</i>

13:38.818 --> 13:40.444
 <i>Thorn got wind of the machine</i>

13:40.486 --> 13:43.280
 <i>and needed to put someone</i>
 <i>in its path.</i>

13:43.322 --> 13:46.492
 <i>He knew we'd never let it</i>
 <i>stay in the private sector.</i>

13:46.534 --> 13:48.118
 <i>Something like that?</i>

13:48.160 --> 13:49.328
 <i>And gave you...</i>

13:49.370 --> 13:51.413
 <i>[whispering] a lot of money.</i>

13:52.790 --> 13:54.333
 <i>[in normal voice] How much?</i>

13:54.375 --> 13:56.377
 <i>More than I'd ever</i>
 <i>seen before, ma'am.</i>

13:57.670 --> 13:59.171
 <i>You murdered someone I...</i>

14:01.006 --> 14:02.007
 <i>raised.</i>

14:03.342 --> 14:06.011
 <i>-He sold you out, ma'am.</i>
 <i>-Someone I raised.</i>

14:06.053 --> 14:07.471
 <i>Clay was going to kill him.</i>

14:07.513 --> 14:10.140
 <i>-You knew what he was?</i>
 <i>-I knew.</i>

14:10.182 --> 14:12.059
 <i>I didn't understand.</i>

14:12.101 --> 14:13.185
 <i>Stop!</i>

14:14.353 --> 14:19.400
 <i>You spared the alien</i>
 <i>and shot the human.</i>

14:19.441 --> 14:23.737
 <i>Spencer's an asset that</i>
 <i>I don't have in my life anymore.</i>

14:23.779 --> 14:26.448
 <i>That's what fucking counts.</i>

14:26.490 --> 14:27.700
 <i>Am I correct?</i>

14:30.077 --> 14:31.203
 <i>Yes, ma'am.</i>

14:33.247 --> 14:34.373
 <i>But I have you.</i>

14:42.923 --> 14:46.051
 <i>I thought about</i>
 <i>throwing you in the hole.</i>

14:46.093 --> 14:49.221
 <i>But I'm giving you a chance</i>
 <i>to make yourself useful.</i>

14:51.056 --> 14:52.433
 <i>A chance.</i>

14:53.934 --> 14:54.977
 <i>Are we clear?</i>

14:55.769 --> 14:57.229
 <i>Yes, ma'am.</i>

14:57.271 --> 15:00.482
 <i>Keep a line on the Falls woman,</i>
 <i>but don't arrest her yet.</i>

15:00.524 --> 15:03.652
 <i>Just see where she takes you.</i>

15:03.694 --> 15:06.405
 <i>She's the one who can</i>
 <i>lead us to both of them</i>

15:06.447 --> 15:08.073
 <i>and quantum fusion.</i>

15:08.782 --> 15:09.783
 <i>Do that,</i>

15:10.701 --> 15:12.578
 <i>or hang for treason.</i>

15:15.205 --> 15:17.416
 <i>They don't hang people</i>
 <i>for treason anymore.</i>

15:18.417 --> 15:19.460
 <i>I do.</i>

15:25.466 --> 15:26.467
 <i>[Newton]</i> <i>You knew</i>

15:27.301 --> 15:29.261
 <i>she'd changed the algorithm.</i>

15:29.303 --> 15:30.971
 <i>[Faraday] I was waiting for her</i>
 <i>to tell me.</i>

15:31.013 --> 15:33.599
 <i>That's very evolved of you.</i>

15:33.641 --> 15:34.683
 <i>Get her back.</i>

15:34.725 --> 15:35.809
 <i>She won't come back.</i>

15:35.851 --> 15:37.770
 <i>She has to. Clock's ticking.</i>

15:37.811 --> 15:39.271
 <i>I have to get home and back</i>

15:39.313 --> 15:41.357
 <i>before this planet</i>
 <i>is too far gone</i>

15:41.398 --> 15:43.901
 <i>in eight fucking years.</i>

15:43.943 --> 15:45.945
 <i>A million things</i>
 <i>could fuck it up.</i>

15:45.986 --> 15:48.614
 <i>-And you have to fully ascend.</i>
 <i>-To what?</i>

15:48.656 --> 15:50.115
 <i>You're about to become legend.</i>

15:50.157 --> 15:51.784
 <i>I thought you were</i>
 <i>paying attention.</i>

15:51.825 --> 15:53.744
 <i>Your little video started it.</i>

15:53.786 --> 15:55.537
 <i>They're buzzing</i>
 <i>with the mystery.</i>

15:55.579 --> 15:57.623
 <i>Like that computer guy</i>
 <i>in black turtlenecks.</i>

15:57.665 --> 15:59.458
 <i>You'll be worshipped.</i>
 <i>You're the next him.</i>

15:59.500 --> 16:01.710
 <i>-You have to be.</i>
 <i>-Why do I have to be?</i>

16:01.752 --> 16:04.296
 <i>Because when we make it back,</i>
 <i>if we make it back,</i>

16:04.338 --> 16:07.007
 <i>someone has to stop them from</i>
 <i>slaughtering us when we land.</i>

16:07.049 --> 16:09.093
 <i>Someone with actual power.</i>

16:09.134 --> 16:10.719
 <i>Someone who is everything</i>
 <i>they wanna be.</i>

16:11.345 --> 16:12.429
 <i>Jesus Christ.</i>

16:12.471 --> 16:14.264
 <i>Exactly.</i>
 <i>Look what they did to him.</i>

16:15.557 --> 16:17.017
 <i>[sighs]</i>

16:17.059 --> 16:20.646
 <i>Do you still not understand</i>
 <i>who they are?</i>

16:24.149 --> 16:25.401
 <i>[sighs]</i>

16:25.442 --> 16:28.237
 <i>I've given you</i>
 <i>ownership of Thorn,</i>

16:28.278 --> 16:30.948
 <i>which now has a controlling</i>
 <i>interest in OriGen.</i>

16:30.990 --> 16:33.200
 <i>They're both yours.</i>
 <i>Congratulations.</i>

16:35.995 --> 16:37.871
 <i>Put my family on the ship.</i>

16:37.913 --> 16:40.290
 <i>My family didn't get</i>
 <i>to go on a ship.</i>

16:40.332 --> 16:43.252
 <i>Put my family on the ship.</i>

16:43.293 --> 16:44.336
 <i>Are you sure?</i>

16:44.378 --> 16:46.130
 <i>You want the wife and kids?</i>

16:46.171 --> 16:49.508
 <i>You might find them</i>
 <i>a bit of a drag now.</i>

16:49.550 --> 16:51.468
 <i>They might not find you at all,</i>

16:51.510 --> 16:54.596
 <i>given that you're fucking</i>
 <i>unrecognizable. [chuckling]</i>

16:54.638 --> 16:56.432
 <i>Why not stick with that girl</i>

16:56.473 --> 16:59.184
 <i>until you wanna kill yourself</i>
 <i>with alcohol?</i>

16:59.226 --> 17:03.022
 <i>Love brings out our latent</i>
 <i>alcoholic tendencies.</i>

17:04.189 --> 17:06.150
 <i>Sister Mary Lou blamed herself,</i>

17:08.027 --> 17:10.279
 <i>but the weakness was yours,</i>

17:11.113 --> 17:12.156
 <i>not hers.</i>

17:12.781 --> 17:13.824
 <i>[sighs]</i>

17:17.494 --> 17:18.537
 <i>Anyway...</i>

17:20.330 --> 17:21.498
 <i>No drones.</i>

17:22.916 --> 17:23.959
 <i>Except me.</i>

17:24.001 --> 17:26.336
 <i>You don't count</i>
 <i>as a drone anymore.</i>

17:35.512 --> 17:37.347
 <i>[Faraday] Is that why</i>
 <i>you brought me?</i>

17:37.389 --> 17:38.474
 <i>You knew I'd end up--</i>

17:38.515 --> 17:39.683
 <i>Best of both.</i>

17:40.309 --> 17:41.435
 <i>How?</i>

17:41.477 --> 17:44.271
 <i>I knew the moment</i>
 <i>you were assigned to me.</i>

17:44.313 --> 17:46.065
 <i>Do you remember the seeds?</i>

17:48.734 --> 17:51.820
 <i>Yeah. It was your last day.</i>

17:51.862 --> 17:53.072
 <i>What did you do?</i>

17:55.574 --> 17:57.034
 <i>I asked questions.</i>

17:57.076 --> 17:59.495
 <i>The only drone ever.</i>

18:05.125 --> 18:06.585
<i>And then we said goodbye.</i>

18:12.591 --> 18:13.675
 <i>[swallows]</i>

18:24.895 --> 18:26.313
 <i>[exhales]</i>

18:26.355 --> 18:27.773
 <i>My children are dead.</i>

18:32.319 --> 18:34.113
 <i>You were light years away.</i>

18:35.823 --> 18:37.825
 <i>[solemn music playing]</i>

18:41.370 --> 18:42.788
 <i>And you were all I had.</i>

18:50.045 --> 18:51.797
 <i>-[thunder rumbling]</i>
 <i>-[birds chirping]</i>

18:57.928 --> 18:59.179
 <i>[cell phone beeping]</i>

18:59.972 --> 19:02.558
 <i>[leaves crackling]</i>

19:06.770 --> 19:08.438
 <i>-Am I real?</i>
 <i>-What?</i>

19:08.480 --> 19:10.607
 <i>Am I a living, breathing--</i>

19:10.649 --> 19:12.151
 <i>It's the fate of the--</i>

19:12.192 --> 19:13.694
 <i>It was my life!</i>

19:13.735 --> 19:14.987
 <i>It was nothing to you!</i>

19:15.028 --> 19:17.573
 <i>It was mine and my family's,</i>
 <i>and you came along</i>

19:17.614 --> 19:19.366
 <i>and just tossed us around</i>
 <i>like you wanted.</i>

19:19.408 --> 19:21.785
 <i>You made us part of your story,</i>

19:21.827 --> 19:23.162
 <i>and here is where you leave us?</i>

19:24.621 --> 19:26.248
 <i>I believed in you...</i>

19:28.041 --> 19:29.793
 <i>but you're not</i>
 <i>who I needed you to be.</i>

19:32.504 --> 19:33.505
 <i>I wanna go home.</i>

19:34.548 --> 19:35.632
 <i>You can't get out of--</i>

19:35.674 --> 19:36.717
 <i>Can't I?</i>

19:37.509 --> 19:38.844
 <i>You can get me home.</i>

19:38.886 --> 19:40.596
 <i>We can go together right now.</i>

19:40.637 --> 19:41.680
 <i>But you won't.</i>

19:43.140 --> 19:44.433
 <i>I can't.</i>

19:44.474 --> 19:46.810
 <i>Not until you unlock</i>
 <i>the algorithm.</i>

19:50.355 --> 19:51.857
 <i>I can never be human.</i>

19:54.193 --> 19:55.652
 <i>I need you to be.</i>

19:55.694 --> 19:57.779
 <i>When you changed the algorithm--</i>

19:57.821 --> 20:00.157
 <i>Yeah. I changed it</i>
 <i>for this moment.</i>

20:00.199 --> 20:01.783
 <i>[Faraday] Exactly.</i>

20:01.825 --> 20:04.620
 <i>A human has to make</i>
 <i>this decision.</i>

20:04.661 --> 20:06.371
 <i>This is the fate of your planet.</i>

20:06.413 --> 20:09.374
 <i>Do you understand I can't live</i>

20:09.416 --> 20:11.960
 <i>if my child</i>
 <i>doesn't recognize me?</i>

20:12.002 --> 20:13.462
 <i>I can't live</i>

20:13.503 --> 20:15.047
 <i>if he turns us into drones.</i>

20:15.088 --> 20:16.215
 <i>That won't happen.</i>

20:17.549 --> 20:18.842
 <i>I promise you.</i>

20:18.884 --> 20:20.969
 <i>I will protect everyone</i>
 <i>from him.</i>

20:21.011 --> 20:22.387
 <i>I will protect Molly.</i>

20:22.429 --> 20:23.513
 <i>How?</i>

20:23.555 --> 20:25.098
 <i>Why should I believe you?</i>

20:25.599 --> 20:26.725
 <i>Because I...</i>

20:30.020 --> 20:31.313
 <i>Because I love her.</i>

20:36.109 --> 20:38.570
 <i>You don't know anything</i>
 <i>about love.</i>

20:39.321 --> 20:40.405
 <i>I learned.</i>

20:40.948 --> 20:42.741
 <i>You learned?</i>

20:42.783 --> 20:44.117
 <i>I didn't have a choice.</i>

20:47.913 --> 20:48.914
 <i>You...</i>

20:51.083 --> 20:53.085
 <i>You picked me up</i>
 <i>from the side of the road</i>

20:53.126 --> 20:54.920
 <i>when you had</i>
 <i>every reason not to.</i>

20:54.962 --> 20:57.256
 <i>When I gave you</i>
 <i>every reason not to.</i>

20:57.297 --> 20:58.757
 <i>But you did it.</i>

20:58.799 --> 21:01.468
 <i>And every day,</i>
 <i>when you braid Molly's hair.</i>

21:02.970 --> 21:04.096
 <i>Her beautiful hair.</i>

21:06.265 --> 21:07.766
 <i>And when your father's skin is</i>

21:08.475 --> 21:10.560
 <i>cracked and dry</i>

21:10.602 --> 21:11.937
 <i>from the medication,</i>

21:11.979 --> 21:13.438
 <i>you help him.</i>

21:13.480 --> 21:14.898
 <i>And the way you forgive me.</i>

21:14.940 --> 21:19.444
 <i>Do you even realize</i>
 <i>what an act of love that is?</i>

21:19.486 --> 21:21.446
 <i>And you do it without thinking.</i>

21:22.739 --> 21:25.284
 <i>So how could I possibly stay</i>

21:25.325 --> 21:29.037
 <i>blind to love around you?</i>

21:32.833 --> 21:34.126
 <i>It's in me.</i>

21:36.128 --> 21:37.713
 <i>I almost believe you.</i>

21:38.839 --> 21:41.466
 <i>Almost has to be enough.</i>

21:43.051 --> 21:44.720
 <i>Otherwise, everyone is gone.</i>

21:45.971 --> 21:47.681
 <i>[breathes deeply]</i>

22:10.329 --> 22:11.663
 <i>[Newton] I'm not sure what</i>
 <i>you said to her,</i>

22:11.705 --> 22:12.831
 <i>but it worked.</i>

22:18.670 --> 22:20.255
 <i>[engine starts]</i>

22:20.297 --> 22:21.548
 <i>She would've been</i>
 <i>the end of you.</i>

22:23.008 --> 22:25.177
 <i>Well done. We have what we need.</i>

22:26.636 --> 22:27.721
 <i>Let's get to work.</i>

22:30.640 --> 22:32.851
 <i>[</i> <i>"Where or When"</i>
 <i>by Lena Horne playing]</i>

22:39.566 --> 22:42.819
<i>It seems we've stood</i>
<i>and talked </i>

22:42.861 --> 22:46.365
<i>Like this before </i>

22:46.406 --> 22:50.535
<i>We looked at each other</i>
<i>in the same way then </i>

22:50.577 --> 22:56.041
<i>But I can't remember</i>
<i>where or when </i>

22:56.083 --> 22:58.043
 <i>[wind chimes tinkling]</i>

22:58.085 --> 23:00.253
<i>The clothes</i>
<i>you're wearing... </i>

23:00.295 --> 23:02.089
 <i>There we go.</i>

23:02.130 --> 23:04.758
 <i>Look at that.</i>
 <i>Look at the wings.</i>

23:04.800 --> 23:06.301
 <i>So beautiful.</i>

23:06.343 --> 23:08.261
<i>The smile you are smiling</i>
<i>you were smiling then </i>

23:08.303 --> 23:10.680
<i>But I can't remember</i>
<i>where or when </i>

23:10.722 --> 23:11.765
 <i>[Molly] Mom!</i>

23:15.185 --> 23:18.271
<i>Some things that happened </i>

23:18.313 --> 23:21.066
<i>For the first time </i>

23:22.609 --> 23:27.072
<i>Seem to be happening again </i>

23:29.699 --> 23:31.576
<i>And so it seems </i>

23:31.618 --> 23:32.744
 <i>It's okay.</i>

23:32.786 --> 23:34.704
<i>That we have met before </i>

23:34.746 --> 23:36.581
 <i>[Justin softly] Dad. Dad.</i>

23:36.623 --> 23:38.875
<i>And laughed before </i>

23:38.917 --> 23:41.002
 <i>Oh, Juzzie.</i>

23:41.044 --> 23:42.087
 <i>[kisses]</i>

23:42.796 --> 23:44.256
 <i>[Josiah chuckles]</i>

23:45.924 --> 23:47.884
 <i>-I'm all right.</i>
 <i>-[whimpers]</i>

23:47.926 --> 23:49.469
 <i>[Josiah] Are you all right?</i>

23:50.637 --> 23:51.638
 <i>Hmm?</i>

23:54.474 --> 23:55.934
 <i>Did you come home alone?</i>

24:01.690 --> 24:02.732
 <i>Molly,</i>

24:03.733 --> 24:05.569
 <i>it's time for my medicine.</i>

24:05.610 --> 24:07.654
 <i>-He's agreeable now.</i>
 <i>-[Josiah chuckles]</i>

24:08.280 --> 24:09.948
 <i>Come. Come on.</i>

24:17.456 --> 24:18.874
 <i>You're gonna go back?</i>

24:18.915 --> 24:20.959
 <i>Hmm? To him?</i>

24:21.751 --> 24:22.836
 <i>Mm, no.</i>

24:24.004 --> 24:25.505
 <i>My part is over.</i>

24:26.047 --> 24:27.299
 <i>[Josiah] Mm-hmm.</i>

24:27.340 --> 24:29.551
 <i>And I can't go back anyway.</i>

24:29.593 --> 24:31.386
 <i>It wasn't what you thought.</i>

24:33.346 --> 24:35.640
 <i>[crying]</i>

24:35.682 --> 24:39.394
 <i>I thought I knew where</i>
 <i>he was taking us, Dad.</i>

24:39.436 --> 24:42.230
 <i>Oh, he's taking me back</i>
 <i>to the same window.</i>

24:47.194 --> 24:49.279
 <i>The view, however,</i>

24:49.321 --> 24:51.573
 <i>is entirely different now.</i>

24:53.617 --> 24:54.868
 <i>-Hmm.</i>
 <i>-[sniffles]</i>

24:57.704 --> 25:00.499
 <i>And what little time</i>
 <i>we have left,</i>

25:00.540 --> 25:03.376
 <i>I'm going to spend it</i>
 <i>believing in him.</i>

25:03.418 --> 25:04.794
 <i>No. I...</i>

25:04.836 --> 25:07.005
 <i>I can't do that anymore, Dad.</i>
 <i>[sniffles]</i>

25:07.839 --> 25:09.049
 <i>Oh, you afraid?</i>

25:09.090 --> 25:10.842
 <i>[whimpers] Yeah.</i>

25:12.093 --> 25:14.054
 <i>I can't believe in something</i>
 <i>I'm afraid of.</i>

25:19.976 --> 25:22.020
 <i>I believe in God</i>

25:23.730 --> 25:26.149
 <i>and gravity... [chuckles]</i>

25:27.776 --> 25:29.486
 <i>And I'm afraid of them both.</i>

25:33.406 --> 25:35.367
 <i>I have faith, Juzzie.</i>

25:38.036 --> 25:39.538
 <i>Because you're a scientist.</i>

25:40.330 --> 25:41.373
 <i>[Josiah chuckles]</i>

25:42.582 --> 25:44.376
 <i>-A great scientist.</i>
 <i>-[Justin chuckles]</i>

25:45.418 --> 25:47.420
 <i>A great scientist.</i>

25:51.091 --> 25:52.133
 <i>[chuckles]</i>

25:53.885 --> 25:55.053
 <i>[Justin sniffles]</i>

26:00.183 --> 26:01.768
 <i>-[indistinct chatter]</i>
 <i>-[phone ringing]</i>

26:01.810 --> 26:04.396
 <i>[woman] Good morning. OriGen.</i>
 <i>Edie Flood's office.</i>

26:04.437 --> 26:07.816
 <i>[Edie] We are in the countdown</i>
 <i>phase to a launch.</i>

26:08.316 --> 26:09.401
 <i>We want a series.</i>

26:09.442 --> 26:11.069
 <i>We would like you to consider</i>

26:11.111 --> 26:12.737
 <i>publishing a series of articles</i>

26:12.779 --> 26:14.656
 <i>on Mr. Faraday, OriGen--</i>

26:14.698 --> 26:16.032
 <i>[Penny] And the machine?</i>

26:16.074 --> 26:17.742
 <i>Absolutely the machine.</i>

26:17.784 --> 26:19.160
 <i>When do I speak with</i>
 <i>Mr. Faraday?</i>

26:19.202 --> 26:20.245
 <i>You'll deal with me.</i>

26:20.287 --> 26:22.706
 <i>Mr. Faraday has been</i>
 <i>providing me</i>

26:22.747 --> 26:24.708
 <i>with information</i>
 <i>regarding whatever it is</i>

26:24.749 --> 26:26.126
 <i>that you've been doing up there.</i>

26:26.167 --> 26:29.254
 <i>In the last three months,</i>
 <i>he's gone silent.</i>

26:29.296 --> 26:30.922
 <i>And the light show.</i>
 <i>That was real?</i>

26:30.964 --> 26:33.675
 <i>The machine is still</i>
 <i>a source of renewable energy</i>

26:33.717 --> 26:35.802
 <i>or has it all just gone to shit?</i>

26:35.844 --> 26:37.304
 <i>No, it hasn't.</i>

26:37.345 --> 26:39.639
 <i>Then why did he stop</i>
 <i>speaking to me?</i>

26:39.681 --> 26:42.142
 <i>Now I imagine</i>
 <i>there are several parties</i>

26:42.183 --> 26:45.186
 <i>who wouldn't want anything</i>
 <i>like this machine to exist.</i>

26:45.228 --> 26:47.606
 <i>Maybe the series that I write</i>

26:47.647 --> 26:51.026
 <i>is about a hapless executive.</i>

26:51.067 --> 26:54.070
 <i>An heiress to shoes</i>
 <i>she can't fill,</i>

26:54.112 --> 26:56.072
 <i>who's now flailing</i>
 <i>in the death throes.</i>

26:56.114 --> 26:58.617
 <i>[Edie] Mr. Faraday and I</i>
 <i>have made an arrangement.</i>

26:58.658 --> 27:00.118
 <i>We're going to</i>
 <i>give you everything</i>

27:00.160 --> 27:01.453
 <i>on the most important</i>
 <i>development in human--</i>

27:01.494 --> 27:02.912
 <i>[Penny] What about Hatch?</i>

27:02.954 --> 27:04.122
 <i>He was the first one</i>
 <i>to reach out to me.</i>

27:04.164 --> 27:05.290
 <i>[Edie] Penny, if you want this,</i>

27:05.332 --> 27:07.000
 <i>Hatch Flood</i>
 <i>does not appear anywhere</i>

27:07.042 --> 27:09.794
 <i>in the legend of Faraday</i>
 <i>and quantum fusion.</i>

27:12.881 --> 27:15.050
 <i>But Hatch brought</i>
 <i>Faraday to OriGen.</i>

27:15.091 --> 27:17.052
 <i>And now you're dealing with me.</i>

27:17.093 --> 27:20.305
 <i>And I am the only direct line</i>
 <i>to Faraday.</i>

27:21.014 --> 27:22.015
 <i>Take it or leave it.</i>

27:22.891 --> 27:24.643
 <i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

27:27.520 --> 27:29.397
 <i>[vehicle approaching]</i>

27:29.439 --> 27:31.149
 <i>[engine stops]</i>

27:31.858 --> 27:33.485
 <i>[hammering]</i>

27:38.031 --> 27:39.032
 <i>[Lisa] Justin.</i>

27:39.908 --> 27:40.950
 <i>I'm alone.</i>

27:45.622 --> 27:46.915
 <i>Get off my property.</i>

27:46.956 --> 27:48.875
 <i>-Please can I talk to you?</i>
 <i>-You wanna talk to me?</i>

27:48.917 --> 27:50.627
 <i>[Dominguez]</i>
 <i>I need to talk to someone.</i>

27:50.669 --> 27:52.587
 <i>I can't tell a priest.</i>

27:52.629 --> 27:54.923
 <i>I can't tell anyone but you.</i>

27:54.964 --> 27:56.758
 <i>You were able to carry all this.</i>

27:56.800 --> 27:59.511
 <i>Everything you know about him</i>
 <i>and you didn't go insane.</i>

28:00.136 --> 28:01.429
 <i>How?</i>

28:01.471 --> 28:03.598
 <i>Well, I didn't torture anyone,</i>
 <i>for starters.</i>

28:07.268 --> 28:09.020
 <i>[Dominguez] I knew</i>
 <i>where he came from.</i>

28:09.062 --> 28:11.356
 <i>But I never saw him</i>
 <i>for what he really was...</i>

28:12.232 --> 28:13.274
 <i>Is.</i>

28:14.275 --> 28:15.485
 <i>He's sent from God.</i>

28:17.529 --> 28:18.530
 <i>And I...</i>

28:19.656 --> 28:22.200
 <i>I tried to sell him out</i>
 <i>for money...</i>

28:23.910 --> 28:25.078
 <i>from an oil company.</i>

28:28.081 --> 28:29.374
 <i>What do you want?</i>

28:29.416 --> 28:30.417
 <i>[Lisa] The CIA,</i>

28:31.292 --> 28:32.335
 <i>they're gonna kill me.</i>

28:33.503 --> 28:35.213
 <i>They have to, eventually.</i>

28:36.673 --> 28:37.882
 <i>But before they do,</i>

28:38.967 --> 28:40.176
 <i>they're gonna take him.</i>

28:41.010 --> 28:42.345
 <i>And when they take him,</i>

28:44.806 --> 28:46.057
 <i>they'll come for you, too.</i>

28:54.649 --> 28:56.818
 <i>You were right about my mother.</i>

28:56.860 --> 28:58.903
 <i>She gave me this</i>

28:58.945 --> 29:01.406
 <i>to make me remember</i>
 <i>that God... [sniffles]</i>

29:02.532 --> 29:03.742
 <i>is always watching.</i>

29:08.246 --> 29:09.497
 <i>Please take it.</i>

29:13.209 --> 29:14.753
 <i>I don't wanna die with it on.</i>

29:18.047 --> 29:19.090
 <i>Please.</i>

29:30.935 --> 29:31.978
 <i>I'm sorry.</i>

29:40.445 --> 29:42.447
 <i>You weren't working</i>
 <i>for an oil company.</i>

29:47.368 --> 29:48.953
 <i>Newton is Thorn.</i>

29:50.371 --> 29:51.414
 <i>[scoffs]</i>

29:53.625 --> 29:55.460
 <i>Does that make it</i>
 <i>better or worse?</i>

30:11.184 --> 30:12.811
 <i>-[jazz music plays over vinyl]</i>
 <i>-[Molly] Grandpa?</i>

30:13.645 --> 30:14.896
 <i>[Josiah] Mm-hmm?</i>

30:16.105 --> 30:17.857
 <i>[Molly] Do you miss your hands?</i>

30:18.483 --> 30:19.567
 <i>No.</i>

30:20.527 --> 30:22.403
 <i>[Molly] Did he take them back?</i>

30:22.445 --> 30:24.823
 <i>-[Josiah] Who?</i>
 <i>-[Molly] The larva.</i>

30:24.864 --> 30:27.408
 <i>Molly girl, come here</i>
 <i>where I can see you.</i>

30:29.536 --> 30:31.871
 <i>I need you</i>
 <i>to remember something.</i>

30:33.039 --> 30:35.583
 <i>The larva is good.</i>

30:35.625 --> 30:38.503
 <i>He is good and he's special.</i>

30:38.545 --> 30:41.005
 <i>He gave me something</i>

30:41.047 --> 30:43.675
 <i>I thought I would</i>
 <i>never have again.</i>

30:44.259 --> 30:46.052
 <i>Things in my...</i>

30:47.387 --> 30:49.055
 <i>imagination.</i>

31:01.276 --> 31:02.861
 <i>If you don't miss your hands,</i>

31:03.486 --> 31:05.196
 <i>then I don't, either.</i>

31:05.238 --> 31:06.865
 <i>-Mm-hmm. [laughs]</i>
 <i>-But I miss your feet.</i>

31:10.034 --> 31:12.829
 <i>[Molly] Mom, Mom.</i>
 <i>Come see Grandpa's hair.</i>

31:12.871 --> 31:15.790
 <i>I'm... I'm house cleaning.</i>

31:15.832 --> 31:17.834
 <i>Has anyone seen</i>
 <i>the cord to my flat iron?</i>

31:17.876 --> 31:19.627
 <i>I hate your flat iron.</i>

31:19.669 --> 31:21.045
 <i>Come see what I did.</i>

31:22.755 --> 31:24.215
 <i>[machine humming]</i>

31:34.350 --> 31:36.060
 <i>[humming continues]</i>

31:41.900 --> 31:42.942
 <i>Mom?</i>

31:50.283 --> 31:51.618
 <i>Oh, man.</i>

31:51.659 --> 31:53.620
 <i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

32:00.585 --> 32:02.086
 <i>[beeping]</i>

32:10.345 --> 32:11.596
 <i>[rapid beeping]</i>

32:54.681 --> 32:56.015
 <i>[Faraday]</i> <i>Justin,</i>

32:56.057 --> 32:59.185
<i>my mission is your mission.</i>

33:00.311 --> 33:01.854
 <i>[male reporter]</i>
<i>The Washington Post's</i>

33:01.896 --> 33:04.607
<i>Penny Morgan has found herself</i>
<i>at the eye of the storm</i>

33:04.649 --> 33:07.694
<i>as the world waits for her</i>
<i>to break her exclusive story.</i>

33:07.735 --> 33:09.404
 <i>[female reporter 1]</i> <i>In news</i>
<i>that set the world on fire,</i>

33:09.445 --> 33:10.822
<i>tech company OriGen Global</i>

33:10.863 --> 33:13.032
<i>will storm London's</i>
<i>Royal Albert Hall tonight.</i>

33:13.074 --> 33:14.367
 <i>[female reporter 2]</i>
<i>After months of speculation,</i>

33:14.409 --> 33:15.660
<i>OriGen's mystery man</i>

33:15.702 --> 33:17.245
<i>will finally reveal himself</i>
<i>to the world</i>

33:17.286 --> 33:19.080
<i>as he unveils what</i>
<i>the company claims</i>

33:19.122 --> 33:20.331
<i>is the missing piece</i>

33:20.373 --> 33:21.457
<i>to a sustainable future.</i>

33:21.499 --> 33:22.667
 <i>[female reporter 3]</i>
<i>When Edie Flood</i>

33:22.709 --> 33:24.002
<i>took over OriGen Global,</i>
<i>she declared,</i>

33:24.043 --> 33:26.421
<i>"This is not</i>
<i>your father's tech company.</i>

33:26.462 --> 33:28.172
<i>It's not my father's, either."</i>

33:28.214 --> 33:32.176
<i>A bold statement she had failed</i>
<i>to live up to, until now.</i>

33:35.388 --> 33:36.931
 <i>[cheers and applause]</i>

33:39.142 --> 33:40.351
 <i>[rumbling]</i>

33:48.901 --> 33:51.362
 <i>[woman]</i> <i>Okay, let's go.</i>
<i>Everybody ready.</i>

33:51.404 --> 33:52.864
<i>Comms check, over.</i>

33:52.905 --> 33:55.366
 <i>[man]</i> <i>Ready in five, four,</i>

33:56.034 --> 33:58.703
<i>three, two, one.</i>

34:00.747 --> 34:01.914
 <i>[audience cheering]</i>

34:04.584 --> 34:07.086
 <i>-[camera shutter clicking]</i>
 <i>-[Edie] Wow. Love you.</i>

34:07.754 --> 34:08.880
 <i>Hello.</i>

34:10.089 --> 34:12.383
 <i>-[cheering continues]</i>
 <i>-It's so good to see you.</i>

34:14.469 --> 34:15.553
 <i>Hmm.</i>

34:16.262 --> 34:18.264
 <i>[chuckles] Okay.</i>

34:22.226 --> 34:23.227
 <i>Hello.</i>

34:24.145 --> 34:26.189
 <i>I'm Edie Flood.</i>

34:26.230 --> 34:28.149
 <i>-[camera shutter clicking]</i>
 <i>-And it is my pleasure</i>

34:28.191 --> 34:29.358
 <i>to be here with you.</i>

34:31.611 --> 34:33.529
 <i>I know what</i>
 <i>you've all been hearing</i>

34:33.571 --> 34:35.573
 <i>and reading</i>
 <i>in the past three months.</i>

34:35.615 --> 34:37.200
 <i>I know the buzz.</i>

34:37.241 --> 34:39.577
 <i>The buzz that is now a clamor.</i>

34:40.286 --> 34:41.788
 <i>I know you have questions.</i>

34:42.955 --> 34:44.916
 <i>I know you have skepticism.</i>

34:44.957 --> 34:47.335
 <i>I know some of you have hearts</i>

34:47.376 --> 34:49.253
 <i>of outright rejection.</i>

34:51.464 --> 34:52.757
 <i>Good.</i>

34:52.799 --> 34:54.258
 <i>We like a challenge.</i>

34:55.051 --> 34:56.094
 <i>My father...</i>

34:58.096 --> 35:00.765
 <i>wanted to make</i>
 <i>the world a better place.</i>

35:01.808 --> 35:02.975
 <i>Simple.</i>

35:03.017 --> 35:04.811
 <i>But I don't think</i>
 <i>he could've imagined</i>

35:04.852 --> 35:06.437
 <i>what we're bringing you today.</i>

35:07.396 --> 35:09.148
 <i>I imagined it.</i>

35:09.190 --> 35:11.818
 <i>A few of us dared to imagine it</i>

35:11.859 --> 35:13.152
 <i>and we've done it.</i>

35:13.194 --> 35:14.570
 <i>We have done it</i>

35:14.612 --> 35:16.447
 <i>and we are here to share it</i>

35:17.406 --> 35:19.659
 <i>-with you.</i>
 <i>-[cheering]</i>

35:21.953 --> 35:23.746
 <i>Please welcome to the stage</i>

35:23.788 --> 35:26.749
 <i>the gentleman you've all</i>
 <i>been so eager to meet,</i>

35:26.791 --> 35:30.586
 <i>Mr. K. Faraday,</i>
 <i>of OriGen Global.</i>

35:30.628 --> 35:32.505
 <i>[audience cheering]</i>

35:50.106 --> 35:51.899
 <i>[cheering subsides]</i>

35:55.528 --> 35:56.821
 <i>[camera shutter clicking]</i>

36:20.219 --> 36:21.345
 <i>How did we get here?</i>

36:24.557 --> 36:25.558
 <i>To this place.</i>

36:28.102 --> 36:29.145
 <i>This moment.</i>

36:30.062 --> 36:31.564
 <i>[sirens blaring]</i>

36:37.570 --> 36:39.322
<i>If we could see</i>
<i>the cosmic shape</i>

36:39.363 --> 36:40.865
<i>of every choice we've made...</i>

36:43.576 --> 36:45.620
<i>would it look like</i>
<i>a straight timeline?</i>

36:48.748 --> 36:49.916
<i>A staircase?</i>

36:52.251 --> 36:53.544
 <i>[siren wailing]</i>

36:53.586 --> 36:55.129
<i>A Mobius strip?</i>

36:59.050 --> 37:00.051
<i>Let's go back,</i>

37:01.093 --> 37:02.136
<i>to the beginning.</i>

37:04.138 --> 37:08.142
<i>I came here because</i>
<i>my choice was simple.</i>

37:08.809 --> 37:10.061
 <i>[siren wailing]</i>

37:10.102 --> 37:13.022
<i>Live or die.</i>

37:16.067 --> 37:18.569
<i>They called me a tyrant.</i>

37:18.611 --> 37:22.073
<i>A king. A tech-god Willy Wonka,</i>

37:22.114 --> 37:25.243
 <i>up to my Gobstoppers in secrets.</i>

37:27.203 --> 37:28.287
 <i>And it's all true.</i>

37:30.164 --> 37:31.207
 <i>Well...</i>

37:32.291 --> 37:34.210
 <i>The secrets part, anyway.</i>

37:36.504 --> 37:38.381
 <i>So, don't say I didn't warn you.</i>

37:38.422 --> 37:40.049
 <i>[siren wailing]</i>

37:52.478 --> 37:54.230
 <i>Where the fuck</i>
 <i>do you think you're going?</i>

37:54.272 --> 37:56.899
 <i>MI5 has to make the arrest.</i>

37:56.941 --> 37:58.401
 <i>[agent 1]</i> <i>All teams,</i>
<i>secure perimeter</i>

37:58.442 --> 37:59.944
<i>and do not apprehend target</i>

37:59.986 --> 38:02.196
<i>until we have visual</i>
<i>confirmation of the device.</i>

38:02.238 --> 38:05.241
<i>Repeat, do not apprehend until</i>
<i>you see the device.</i>

38:05.283 --> 38:06.284
 <i>[man] Copy.</i>

38:07.201 --> 38:08.577
 <i>[audience murmuring]</i>

38:19.338 --> 38:21.132
 <i>Someone get me my fucking phone.</i>

38:21.799 --> 38:23.301
 <i>[murmuring continues]</i>

38:26.637 --> 38:28.472
 <i>The immediate problem is,</i>

38:29.473 --> 38:32.852
 <i>my friends at the CIA,</i>

38:34.145 --> 38:36.022
 <i>MI5,</i>

38:36.063 --> 38:37.481
 <i>think that they are</i>
 <i>the only ones</i>

38:37.523 --> 38:39.483
 <i>who are entitled to secrets.</i>

38:39.525 --> 38:41.193
 <i>They are desperate to discover</i>

38:41.235 --> 38:43.696
 <i>how I built what I am here</i>
 <i>to give you,</i>

38:43.738 --> 38:45.948
 <i>so they can keep you</i>
 <i>where you are.</i>

38:46.699 --> 38:48.326
 <i>Visual target.</i>

38:48.367 --> 38:49.744
 <i>[Faraday]</i> <i>Mercy exists</i>

38:49.785 --> 38:51.829
<i>when we are able</i>
<i>to truly see each other,</i>

38:52.872 --> 38:54.540
<i>and ourselves.</i>

38:54.582 --> 38:56.167
<i>So does power.</i>

38:56.208 --> 38:57.460
 <i>[audience shouting]</i>

38:57.501 --> 38:59.670
 <i>Well, if they say</i>
 <i>my words are weapons,</i>

38:59.712 --> 39:02.131
 <i>then let this be</i>
 <i>a declaration of war.</i>

39:02.173 --> 39:03.841
 <i>[audience shouting]</i>

39:03.883 --> 39:06.427
 <i>Are you ready</i>
 <i>to get your hands bloody?</i>

39:06.469 --> 39:07.762
 <i>[audience] Yeah!</i>

39:07.803 --> 39:09.597
 <i>When people talk about my work,</i>

39:09.638 --> 39:11.599
 <i>I hear words like "revolution."</i>

39:11.640 --> 39:12.683
 <i>Well, today,</i>

39:13.476 --> 39:15.353
 <i>this one drops the "R."</i>

39:16.771 --> 39:18.939
 <i>In this box,</i>

39:18.981 --> 39:21.525
 <i>I hold the next step</i>
 <i>on the great timeline.</i>

39:23.486 --> 39:25.988
 <i>The power they've ripped away</i>

39:27.031 --> 39:28.908
 <i>will be returned to us.</i>

39:28.949 --> 39:31.243
 <i>No restrictions, no conditions.</i>

39:31.285 --> 39:33.371
 <i>We will finally be free.</i>

39:33.412 --> 39:34.538
 <i>Are you ready?</i>

39:34.580 --> 39:35.581
 <i>[audience] Yeah!</i>

39:37.875 --> 39:39.293
 <i>[Faraday]</i> <i>Are you ready?</i>

39:39.335 --> 39:41.087
 <i>Mm, yeah.</i>

39:41.128 --> 39:43.172
 <i>Go, take him, now.</i>

39:43.214 --> 39:46.175
 <i>Are you ready</i>
 <i>to choose the next step</i>

39:46.217 --> 39:47.551
 <i>in human...</i>

39:49.053 --> 39:50.054
 <i>evolution?</i>

39:51.806 --> 39:53.849
 <i>[audience cheering]</i>

39:58.729 --> 40:00.731
 <i>[cheering continues]</i>

40:05.861 --> 40:07.905
 <i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

40:48.195 --> 40:49.238
 <i>[door beeps]</i>

41:10.342 --> 41:11.385
 <i>[sighs]</i>

41:15.139 --> 41:16.640
 <i>Where's Thomas Newton?</i>

41:21.270 --> 41:22.813
 <i>[breathes deeply]</i>

41:24.273 --> 41:28.444
 <i>Please bring Justin Falls</i>
 <i>and Hatch Flood</i>

41:28.486 --> 41:30.404
 <i>to this room. I know</i>
 <i>you've brought them here--</i>

41:30.446 --> 41:33.073
 <i>How many of these are there?</i>

41:35.117 --> 41:36.327
 <i>That depends on you.</i>

41:37.286 --> 41:38.412
 <i>On me?</i>

41:38.454 --> 41:40.080
 <i>Until I know</i>
 <i>they're still alive,</i>

41:40.122 --> 41:42.791
 <i>there is no point</i>
 <i>to our negotiation.</i>

41:42.833 --> 41:44.710
 <i>We're not negotiating.</i>

41:44.752 --> 41:45.961
 <i>Then why am I here?</i>

41:53.928 --> 41:56.680
 <i>-Thank you.</i>
 <i>-How many cubes are out there?</i>

41:56.722 --> 41:58.516
 <i>-I'm going home.</i>
 <i>-Say again?</i>

41:58.557 --> 42:01.977
 <i>I'm going back to my planet</i>

42:02.019 --> 42:06.023
 <i>and bringing what's left</i>
 <i>of my species here.</i>

42:06.065 --> 42:07.858
 <i>They're not coming here.</i>

42:08.484 --> 42:09.527
 <i>Let me explain.</i>

42:09.568 --> 42:11.487
 <i>I would have to allow it.</i>

42:11.529 --> 42:13.864
 <i>And you have nothing to offer.</i>

42:13.906 --> 42:16.200
 <i>I already have a cube.</i>

42:17.201 --> 42:18.536
 <i>If there's another one</i>
 <i>out there,</i>

42:18.577 --> 42:20.538
 <i>someone's going to have to</i>
 <i>take a crash course</i>

42:20.579 --> 42:22.915
 <i>in spaceman before</i>
 <i>they can figure it out.</i>

42:23.874 --> 42:26.544
 <i>I already have you.</i>

42:27.253 --> 42:30.047
 <i>I have the architect.</i>

42:30.089 --> 42:33.884
 <i>And I already have the only</i>
 <i>road to mass production,</i>

42:34.426 --> 42:35.886
 <i>OriGen Global.</i>

42:36.428 --> 42:37.429
 <i>[door buzzes]</i>

42:55.281 --> 42:59.952
 <i>[Faraday] Thorn Oil now holds</i>
 <i>the majority stake in OriGen.</i>

42:59.994 --> 43:03.163
 <i>Your people behind the glass</i>
 <i>know what that means.</i>

43:03.205 --> 43:05.874
 <i>The CIA can't touch it anymore.</i>

43:06.500 --> 43:07.543
 <i>And Thorn...</i>

43:08.752 --> 43:10.629
 <i>belongs to me.</i>

43:10.671 --> 43:13.173
 <i>-Control of both companies...</i>
 <i>-Check it.</i>

43:13.215 --> 43:16.218
 <i>...is being transferred</i>
 <i>to Justin Falls</i>

43:16.260 --> 43:19.013
 <i>and Hatch Flood.</i>

43:19.054 --> 43:21.348
 <i>Wait, no. What...</i>
 <i>What about Edie?</i>

43:21.390 --> 43:24.351
 <i>Your sister has served</i>
 <i>her purpose for me.</i>

43:24.393 --> 43:25.936
 <i>She's out.</i>

43:25.978 --> 43:27.938
 <i>Thomas Newton chose me</i>

43:27.980 --> 43:29.607
 <i>and I'm choosing you.</i>

43:31.400 --> 43:33.694
 <i>These two have just become</i>

43:33.736 --> 43:37.114
 <i>the most important people</i>
 <i>on the planet.</i>

43:37.156 --> 43:38.532
 <i>I need to lift off</i>

43:38.574 --> 43:42.119
 <i>and land without being</i>
 <i>shot out of the sky.</i>

43:42.161 --> 43:45.623
 <i>And the Antheans</i>
 <i>will need asylum.</i>

43:48.334 --> 43:49.335
 <i>All of them.</i>

43:51.587 --> 43:55.758
 <i>Then I'm putting the three</i>
 <i>of you in a hole, forever.</i>

43:55.799 --> 43:58.093
 <i>It doesn't matter</i>
 <i>that you control Thorn.</i>

43:58.135 --> 43:59.803
 <i>We do what we want.</i>

43:59.845 --> 44:02.348
 <i>So, it's all ours now.</i>

44:03.349 --> 44:04.975
 <i>And if your friends show up,</i>

44:05.017 --> 44:08.771
 <i>they're going in our version</i>
 <i>of foster care.</i>

44:08.812 --> 44:12.107
 <i>You weren't banking</i>
 <i>on my humanity, were you?</i>

44:12.149 --> 44:13.150
 <i>Of course not.</i>

44:14.360 --> 44:16.028
 <i>I'm banking on your greed.</i>

44:16.779 --> 44:17.988
 <i>In 12 hours,</i>

44:18.030 --> 44:21.158
 <i>the specs and algorithm</i>
 <i>for quantum fusion</i>

44:21.200 --> 44:23.243
 <i>will be released</i>
 <i>on the Internet.</i>

44:23.285 --> 44:25.746
 <i>Everyone, everywhere on Earth,</i>

44:25.788 --> 44:28.582
 <i>will have it... for free.</i>

44:28.624 --> 44:30.125
 <i>Oh, don't be ridiculous.</i>

44:30.167 --> 44:32.336
 <i>[Faraday] The design</i>
 <i>has already been distributed</i>

44:32.378 --> 44:36.507
 <i>across 117,000 servers</i>
 <i>on a time release</i>

44:36.548 --> 44:38.676
 <i>in data centers</i>
 <i>all over the world.</i>

44:39.551 --> 44:42.346
 <i>I can stop it, or release it,</i>

44:43.222 --> 44:46.308
 <i>at any time, from anywhere.</i>

44:46.350 --> 44:50.562
 <i>Hatch, please tell them</i>
 <i>what happens after that.</i>

44:53.482 --> 44:54.608
 <i>Well...</i>

44:55.734 --> 44:57.027
 <i>Hatch.</i>

44:57.069 --> 44:58.529
 <i>Uh, yeah, okay.</i>

44:58.570 --> 45:01.532
 <i>Um, well, if the Chinese and</i>
 <i>the Russians have the specs,</i>

45:01.573 --> 45:03.659
 <i>and the Chinese build things</i>
 <i>faster than we do,</i>

45:03.701 --> 45:07.162
 <i>then in this global race</i>
 <i>to weaponize, you lose.</i>

45:07.204 --> 45:08.956
 <i>And then every</i>
 <i>terrorist organization,</i>

45:08.997 --> 45:11.583
 <i>and every hacker</i>
 <i>with a credit card will...</i>

45:11.625 --> 45:14.128
 <i>I mean, in a week, maybe two,</i>

45:14.169 --> 45:16.171
 <i>the US will no longer</i>
 <i>be a superpower.</i>

45:16.213 --> 45:17.881
 <i>If this thing were an octopus,</i>

45:17.923 --> 45:20.843
 <i>then its tentacles</i>
 <i>would be the economy,</i>

45:20.884 --> 45:23.762
 <i>weapons, the actual map,</i>
 <i>the military,</i>

45:23.804 --> 45:25.723
 <i>power grids,</i>
 <i>transportation hubs,</i>

45:25.764 --> 45:27.391
 <i>all science, all commerce,</i>

45:27.433 --> 45:28.809
 <i>all medicine, all government--</i>

45:28.851 --> 45:30.394
 <i>-That's more than eight.</i>
 <i>-Oh, I'm sorry,</i>

45:30.436 --> 45:32.438
 <i>I... I lost count,</i>
 <i>'cause I'm fuckin' terrified.</i>

